Hi Zach

The weird marks on the back of the Leifield is from a wet sheet transfer. Basically the ink was still wet when they stacked the sheets. The blue ink on the back are the stripes from Leifield's sleeves. Same with the green ink on the lower portion of the card.

Neat card and good luck with the sale.


Jantz
